section_title: Issues relating to the implementation of Protocol Article 2.3
sentences: Regarding implementation of Protocol Article 2.3 (adverse effects of P&Ms), Chair Thorgeirsson said there was no agreement.
SBSTA adopted the conclusions, noting lack of agreement (FCCC/SBSTA/2003/L.24).
enb_long_title: Ninth Conference of the Parties to the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change
